data.description: SELLERS OFFERING A $12K CREDIT TO BUYER AND $1K BUYER BROKER BONUS!!! Experience elegant living in this stunning Pulte Patagonia model nestled inside a gated community. Enjoy breathtaking VIEWS and $100K in upgrades, including a culinary kitchen with stainless steel appliances, an executive island and cafe cabinet with quartz countertops. Two en suites provide privacy, while the owner's suite boasts a spa-like bathroom and large walk-in closet. The flexible layout also includes two guest bedrooms, a FLEX room and den for versatile living. The property's charm continues outdoors ideal for entertainment & relaxation. A three-car garage provides ample space for vehicles, storage needs or creating a workshop. Close to I-40.  Make it yours today and move in before the New Year. Welcome home!
